{
  "texts": [
    "Let's first consider the outcome of the three cases under the STAY protocol.",
    "(a) If the prize is behind Door 1, you win.",
    "If it is behind Door 2 or 3, you lose.",
    "(b) Hence there is a 1 3 chance of winning if you follow STAY. 4.",
    "The cases are a bit more complex if you follow SWITCH, because, crucially, Monty knows where the prize is, and, having perceived your initial choice, will always reveal a door without the prize behind it."
  ]
}